00:15:31,080 --> 00:15:33,600
with regard to being ready for the battle

252
00:15:33,600 --> 00:15:34,880
that we're engaged in.

253
00:15:34,880 --> 00:15:37,840
He says this, that you may be able to withstand

254
00:15:37,840 --> 00:15:41,440
in the evil day, and having done all to stand.

