00:16:14,320 --> 00:16:15,600
And you can rest assured,

268
00:16:15,600 --> 00:16:17,040
you can know with certainty

269
00:16:17,040 --> 00:16:18,920
that he's gonna continue to fire

270
00:16:18,920 --> 00:16:21,560
as many of these fiery darts as he can.

271
00:16:21,560 --> 00:16:23,760
But we have that shield of faith.

272
00:16:23,760 --> 00:16:26,680
The Bible continues and says this in verse 17,

273
00:16:26,680 --> 00:16:28,440
and take the helmet of salvation

274
00:16:28,440 --> 00:16:33,440
and the sword of the spirit, which is the word of God.

275
00:16:33,800 --> 00:16:37,140
Oh, I'm so thankful for the whole armor of God.

276
00:16:37,140 --> 00:16:40,000
Every morning of our lives, every day of our lives,

277
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:43,680
we must take the admonition that God has given us

278
00:16:43,680 --> 00:16:47,040
in his precious word, and if we're going to stand,

279
00:16:47,040 --> 00:16:49,520
if we're going to stand in the gap,

280
00:16:49,520 --> 00:16:52,720
we must put on the whole armor of God.

281
00:16:53,880 --> 00:16:57,800
It'd be foolish to see someone that is in military,

282
00:16:57,800 --> 00:17:01,800
law enforcement, to enter into their workplace

283
00:17:01,800 --> 00:17:05,740
without the proper protection, without their armor,

284
00:17:05,740 --> 00:17:10,380
without the items that have been provided for them

285
00:17:10,380 --> 00:17:13,460
to give them safety, to help them in the line of work

286
00:17:14,240 --> 00:17:15,080
in which they're engaged in.

287
00:17:15,080 --> 00:17:16,340
You think about playing sports.

288
00:17:16,340 --> 00:17:19,300
I played sports as a child, as a teenager,

289
00:17:19,300 --> 00:17:22,020
and in sports, there are pieces of equipment

290
00:17:22,020 --> 00:17:24,220
that you put on to protect yourself,

