00:18:24,060 --> 00:18:26,020
that would stand in the gap carry with it

315
00:18:26,020 --> 00:18:28,020
the idea of standing for truth and right,

316
00:18:28,020 --> 00:18:29,580
but I believe also it carries with it

317
00:18:29,580 --> 00:18:32,360
the idea of standing as an intercessor.

318
00:18:33,820 --> 00:18:34,660
It's amazing to me,

319
00:18:34,660 --> 00:18:36,140
as you begin to think about the Old Testament,

320
00:18:36,140 --> 00:18:37,739
you begin to think about the example,

321
00:18:37,739 --> 00:18:39,600
I'll just use the example of Moses

322
00:18:39,600 --> 00:18:41,840
and what a great intercessor he was

323
00:18:41,840 --> 00:18:43,640
for the nation of Israel.

324
00:18:43,640 --> 00:18:45,360
I begin to think about the truth

325
00:18:45,360 --> 00:18:48,059
of the passage of scripture here in Ephesians 6,

326
00:18:48,059 --> 00:18:50,080
that we've looked at the whole armor of God

327
00:18:50,080 --> 00:18:51,880
and how that immediately,

328
00:18:51,880 --> 00:18:55,119
it transfers from being the whole armor of God

329
00:18:55,119 --> 00:18:56,860
and putting on the whole armor of God

330
00:18:56,860 --> 00:18:59,880
to the very next verse of scripture in verse number 18,

331
00:18:59,880 --> 00:19:02,520
praying always

332
00:19:04,739 --> 00:19:07,520
with all prayer and supplication in the spirit

333
00:19:07,520 --> 00:19:10,160
and watching thereunto with all perseverance

334
00:19:10,160 --> 00:19:11,480
and supplication.

335
00:19:11,480 --> 00:19:14,360
Notice what the last three words of verse number 18 are,

336
00:19:14,360 --> 00:19:17,940
for all saints.

337
00:19:17,940 --> 00:19:18,780
You know what that is?

338
00:19:18,780 --> 00:19:20,360
That's intercessory prayer.

339
00:19:21,400 --> 00:19:23,280
That's praying for the brethren.

340
00:19:23,280 --> 00:19:25,920
And I believe that if we're to stand in the gap,

341
00:19:25,920 --> 00:19:28,500
that we stand not only for truth and right,

342
00:19:28,500 --> 00:19:30,800
but we stand as an intercessor,

343
00:19:30,800 --> 00:19:32,720
that we understand the importance

344
00:19:32,720 --> 00:19:34,440
and the priority of prayer,

345
00:19:34,440 --> 00:19:37,420
that we understand that God has ordained it,

346
00:19:38,200 --> 00:19:39,739
that prayer moves His hand,

347
00:19:39,739 --> 00:19:42,739
and we understand as we look to the scriptures,

348
00:19:42,739 --> 00:19:44,320
as we look to the word of God,

349
00:19:44,320 --> 00:19:48,340
so many examples of how God intervened

350
00:19:48,340 --> 00:19:50,160
because somebody prayed.

351
00:19:52,619 --> 00:19:55,300
Standing in the gap requires

352
00:19:55,300 --> 00:19:57,500
that we'd stand for truth and right.

353
00:19:57,500 --> 00:20:00,260
It requires that we'd stand as an intercessor.

354
00:20:00,260 --> 00:20:03,920
that we would be engaged in intercessory prayer.

355
00:20:03,920 --> 00:20:05,720
I challenged you last Sunday evening

356
00:20:05,720 --> 00:20:09,120
as I passed out a sheet with all of those

357
00:20:09,120 --> 00:20:11,160
that had registered at that point

