00:20:26,560 --> 00:20:28,320
but the other four days that I was here

365
00:20:28,360 --> 00:20:31,120
to be able to say, I've prayed for you.

366
00:20:31,120 --> 00:20:33,700
I prayed for you by name.

367
00:20:36,440 --> 00:20:38,520
That we'd stand in the gap.

368
00:20:38,520 --> 00:20:41,020
Standing for truth and for right.

369
00:20:42,260 --> 00:20:45,200
Standing as an intercessor.

