00:21:38,640 --> 00:21:40,500
I'll give you two thoughts with regard

390
00:21:40,500 --> 00:21:42,180
to executing judgment.

391
00:21:42,180 --> 00:21:45,060
One is this, one who simply does right.

392
00:21:46,700 --> 00:21:47,780
That does right.

